results.description:
White Rock lake, Sunset Bay
Down The Hatch
This grebe popped up out of nowhere in front of me and was in the process of swallowing its catch.  Then it dived again and didn't come back up until it was a long ways off.  The back looks silver because there is a layer of water on it still.
